text: Eduardo Campbell (born 2 July 1933) is a Panamanian wrestler. He competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Panamanian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Panama Category:Wrestlers at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in wrestling Category:Pan American Games silver medalists for Panama Category:Wrestlers at the 1959 Pan American Games Category:Wrestlers at the 1963 Pan American Games
